cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.CR

This paper discusses the use of unmanned aerial vehicles and drones to enhance network coverage and capacity in cellular networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses the use of novel radio resource management techniques, which could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions safety operations and reliability, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
